base.Title: AMIRI CRYSTAL BALL TEE BLACK
base.Body (HTML): Throughout AMIRI’s Spring/Summer 2023 collection, you’ll see myriad references to the occult and the art of fortune telling – with the crystal ball graphic that defines this T-shirt perhaps being the most obvious. It’s this ability to find inspiration in time-honoured art and practices and render it suited to the streetwear crowd that confirms the label’s cult status season after season.
